snippet.title: Rogue Legacy 2 - Official Animated Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the gorgeous animated release date trailer for Rogue Legacy 2, the upcoming roguelike sequel that will be available for PC, Xbox One, and Xbox Series X/S on April 28.

#IGN #Gaming
